  <summary date="2017-03-30T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Small Business Tax Equity Act of 2017

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt a trade or business that conducts marijuana sales in compliance with state law from the prohibition against allowing business-related tax credits or deductions for expenditures in connection with trafficking in controlled substances.</summary>
